description:
&lt;p&gt;We are currently seeking Physiotherapists at Band 5 level to join our rotational scheme.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer excellent opportunities for new graduates and experienced band 5’s wanting to enhance their skills. We offer strong professional leadership and rotations across East and North Hertfordshire, working in partnership with Hertfordshire Community NHS Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post covers Acute Trust rotations at Lister Hospital, Stevenage which includes respiratory care, including on call opportunities; orthopaedics; care of the elderly; stroke/hyperacute stroke unit; general medical wards and rapid response discharge home to assess team . Our Hertfordshire Community Trust rotations are Bed based rehabilitation, core community therapy and MSK based at Stevenage, Letchworth, Royston, Welwyn Garden City, Hertford and Waltham Cross with highly skilled, experienced senior staff to support.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You will be joining a substantial Band 5 workforce with excellent peer support. We are looking for sound clinical reasoning and communication skills, an ability to work within a team and to use your initiative.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Hertfordshire is a very pleasant county with close proximity to London. There is an excellent transport system into London Kings Cross from Stevenage with fast trains taking 20 minutes and a good train service to Cambridge. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Natasha Tanner, Clinical Service Lead&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address : natashatanner@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number : 01438 284074&lt;/p&gt;
